{"type":"message","id":"7bcfc136","parentId":"1a2f4eb2","timestamp":"2026-04-27T14:05:10.279Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze:\n\nGmail - 2 new emails:\n1. eufy newsletter - PROMOTIONS - LOW PRIORITY\n2. ZipRecruiter - SPECTRUM job opening - IMPORTANT\n\niCloud - 3 emails total. The flags column shows which ones are unread (no flags = unread). Let me check:\n- ID 8: no flags - UNREAD (new today!)\n- ID 7: R flag - READ\n- ID 6: R flag - READ\n\nSo only ID 8 is new/unread. Let me read it.\n\nLet me read the iCloud email to get details.\n","thinkingSignature":"4b24813cbea6329e0e5ffa0696fec0dd524aaed4095e0028d94b78570a01aa7d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0mwdn9tnvcsu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read 8 --account icloud 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":419,"output":167,"cacheRead":19584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20170,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777298689183,"responseId":"063ea001e2b0e9205fc0c682292c8732"}}
{"type":"message","id":"849989ab","parentId":"7bcfc136","timestamp":"2026-04-27T14:05:11.626Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0mwdn9tnvcsu_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[2m2026-04-27T14:05:11.321759Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T14:05:11.322512Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T14:05:11.322532Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T14:05:11.322578Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHi Amy, I wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part o\nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\n\nHi Amy,\n\n\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\n\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\n\n\nThank you,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1332,"aggregated":"[2m2026-04-27T14:05:11.321759Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T14:05:11.322512Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T14:05:11.322532Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-27T14:05:11.322578Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHi Amy, I wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part o\nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\n\nHi Amy,\n\n\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\n\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\n\n\nThank you,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777298711626}}
{"type":"message","id":"2d702ab9","parentId":"849989ab","timestamp":"2026-04-27T14:05:22.548Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the info I need. Let me compose and send both messages.\n\n**Gmail - 2 new emails:**\n1. eufy newsletter - LOW PRIORITY (promotions)\n2. ZipRecruiter - IMPORTANT (job opportunity for SPECTRUM)\n\n**iCloud - 1 new email (unread, ID 8):**\n1. RC Leasing - IMPORTANT (apartment application follow-up, asking when they want to move)\n\nLet me send both messages back-to-back.\n","thinkingSignature":"cdea9d7c909ae52d6b11af5acf259367856ebc378741f593053dc5d62fba3346"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l0jiqwdmq7h1_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"telegram","message":"📬 GMAIL — New Mail (2 new)\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• ZipRecruiter — Bobby, SPECTRUM has an open position\n  └ Job alert: SPECTRUM has a position matching your profile. Click to view details.\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• eufy — Plus Member Benefits Are Better Than Ever!\n  └ Newsletter promoting eufy Plus membership benefits.","target":"8212808444"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":681,"output":243,"cacheRead":19968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20892,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777298711630,"responseId":"063ea017b3622a6b97c6236846d1ffcd"}}
